---
import DefaultLayout from '@/layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';
import { Background } from '@/components/background';
import { AnimatedGrid } from '@/components/animated-grid';
---

<DefaultLayout title="About - Hooklyne" description="Two founders who got tired of the same problem. Hooklyne is what we built to fix it.">
  <Background>
    <AnimatedGrid client:only="react" />
    <section class="py-28 lg:py-32 lg:pt-48">
      <div class="container max-w-3xl">

        {/* Badge */}
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-full border border-[#344ca3]/20 bg-[#344ca3]/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#344ca3] uppercase tracking-wide">
            About us
          </span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-[#022f51] text-4xl tracking-tight md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-6">
          We got tired of the<br />same problem.
        </h1>

        <p class="text-[#64748b] text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Both of us work in B2B sales. We've seen the same thing at every company: the research takes longer than the outreach. You spend hours finding the right company, finding the right person, figuring out what to say - and by the time you're ready, the moment has passed.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#64748b] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The tools that exist either give you raw data and expect you to do the work, or they're built for enterprise teams with SDR armies and six-figure contracts. There was nothing in the middle - nothing that worked for a 15-person Dutch company with two sales reps and a full pipeline to manage.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#64748b] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          So we built it.
        </p>

        {/* Divider */}
        <div class="border-t border-[#e2e8f0] mb-12"></div>

        {/* Founders */}
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 mb-16">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-6">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-[#022f51] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white text-lg font-bold">J</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#022f51] font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Joey</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#344ca3] font-medium mb-3">Co-founder</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">
              Background in SaaS, sales consulting, and building products. Has run outreach campaigns across verticals and got obsessed with why the research step was still broken in 2024.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-6">
            <div class="size-12 rounded-xl bg-[#344ca3] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-white text-lg font-bold">T</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[#022f51] font-semibold text-lg mb-1">Tim</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-[#344ca3] font-medium mb-3">Co-founder</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">
              Sales background in the Dutch market, deep in B2B account development. Knows exactly how Dutch buyers think and what makes outreach land - or get ignored.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* What we believe */}
        <div class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-[#022f51] text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">What we believe</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {[
              {
                title: "Quality over quantity",
                body: "Call 5 prepared, don't blast 1,000. The best outreach is specific, timely, and relevant - not a numbers game. Hooklyne is built around this principle.",
              },
              {
                title: "Outreach should sound like you",
                body: "Generic templates get ignored. We write in your voice, referencing real signals about the prospect. It takes more effort to build - but the results speak for themselves.",
              },
              {
                title: "Dutch B2B deserves better tooling",
                body: "Most sales intelligence tools are built for the US market, in English, for enterprise teams. The Dutch SME market has been underserved. We're fixing that.",
              },
              {
                title: "You shouldn't need to interpret data",
                body: "Tools that give you a data dump and expect you to figure it out aren't saving you time. Hooklyne delivers finished work - not raw intelligence to analyse.",
              },
            ].map((item) => (
              <div class="flex gap-4 rounded-xl border border-[#e2e8f0] bg-white p-5">
                <div class="mt-0.5 size-2 rounded-full bg-[#ff8c42] shrink-0"></div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#022f51] mb-1">{item.title}</h4>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[#64748b] leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* CTA */}
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[#344ca3]/20 bg-[#344ca3]/4 p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-[#022f51] text-xl font-semibold mb-2">We're running a pilot</h3>
          <p class="text-[#64748b] text-sm mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
            10 fully researched prospect packages, all features included, in exchange for a feedback call. No credit card.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
            style="background-color: #022f51"
          >
            Request pilot access
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>
  </Background>
</DefaultLayout>
